snippet.title: Champion Unmasked: Krypto
snippet.description:
Do you want to guard your allies with unmatched ferocity? Sign up and play Infinite Crisis for free today at http://www.infinitecrisis.com!

Be the top dog of Coast City's bottom lane as Krypto, the Superdog! Krypto joins the Infinite Crisis roster on March 26th, the same day as our Steam launch!
